(00852)
Bloom ? You know where all the sorrows lie ? It’s your birthday and I can't even make a wish to you ; Of course you are connected to me ! I can text you whenever I want ! Bt the barrier you put away in front of me might seem invisible bt its way too much strong ! I had to kill the love of my life in my very own hand , It's way too much heartbreaking than anyone can ever think ;

 Happy Birthday
